<h3 id="toc0"><span>CODE 192-DCLS - RESTRICTED GENERAL FOUNDATION USE</span></h3>
<p>RAISA (Records and Information Security Administration) has declassified portions of the following posthumous text under Code 192-DCLS for the purpose of &quot;making available defunct, inaccurate, outdated, or compromised texts by deceased authors for general usage, research, and analysis by Foundation assets and Foundation-approved affiliates&quot; in compliance with §4.11 of Protocol AXNN-53 (&quot;Declassification of Internal Research&quot;).</p>
