<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:1.4em;">PRACTICAL LOGOPSYCHOLOGY (1998)</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="font-size:1em;"><em>████ Thorn and █████ Włonsky</em></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>CONTENTS

Foreword   1

Chapter 0.0: Preface   2

Chapter 0.1: Theory and practice   5

Chapter 0.2: Logomemetic primers throughout history   112  

Chapter 0.3: Practical categorization of primers   196

Chapter 0.4: Constructing command primers in the field   245

Chapter 0.5: Usage of primers in the Creation   355

Chapter 0.6: Administration of command primers to large populations    533

